Class FieldException

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Throwable
java.lang.Exception
org.interworldtransport.cladosFExceptions.FieldException
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
FieldBinaryException
public class FieldException extends Exception
This class is designed to be the top of the Field exception family. All instances of descendants are assumed to originate from Field related problems. Common elements from each exception class are found here.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Dr Alfred W Differ
